{"tid":2382210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"長得好看的人什麼髮型都適合！《女神降臨》「秀雅」姜旻兒短髮超可愛、長髮是辣妹啊！","createTime":"2021-01-27T06:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T10:30:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07937a7d97f48c15fa26a27ba58914f6561792f3","tid":2382210,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_165928a56f52ef618bdbb39c58ca98e2/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-895000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_165928a56f52ef618bdbb39c58ca98e2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-895000.jpg&h=78c48a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有看《女神降臨》的朋友們，一定都喜歡秀雅（姜旻兒 飾）這個角色吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她擁有瘋狂親和力，在朱靜（文佳煐 飾）轉學到自己班上後，馬上與她成為好友。12集尾聲，朱靜素顏的秘密被曝光，秀雅知道後也很生氣，因為覺得朱靜沒有告訴她這件事情，是不把她當成好朋友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_be73bc37d820eaa917f49339ac02dfa5/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894987.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_be73bc37d820eaa917f49339ac02dfa5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894987.png&h=550c26c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_111878f2cb6f0c23f68fb624e8f5f148/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894988.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_111878f2cb6f0c23f68fb624e8f5f148%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894988.png&h=586bc47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖：黃Viu煲劇平台）<br />\n<br />\n劇中，姜旻兒以短髮造型亮相，整個超有辨識度。而她常通過IG（minah320_97 ）分享日常生活，長髮造型也很美，果然美女不管什麼髮型都好看啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f317918dbcaa06488ba6156210efbc48/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f317918dbcaa06488ba6156210efbc48%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894999.jpg&h=a2aba8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0c71dddbe312b0fa12f24d9986de8513/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894990.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0c71dddbe312b0fa12f24d9986de8513%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894990.jpg&h=90c00956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b5718fa9df34119101708e4033021e0b/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b5718fa9df34119101708e4033021e0b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894991.jpg&h=40ee9394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c1ff6f8805fabf9d4a8b80f76ab3a32a/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c1ff6f8805fabf9d4a8b80f76ab3a32a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894993.jpg&h=2ec47ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_45c1118443c0189b5e6c9ed75fca5697/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894992.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_45c1118443c0189b5e6c9ed75fca5697%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894992.jpg&h=13c895dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖：IG@minah320_97）<br />\n<br />\n而1997年出生的姜旻兒在2012年以演員開始活動，曾出演《張玉貞，為愛而生》飾演金泰希少年時期、《無理的前進》飾演朴多美、《A-TEEN 2》飾演車雅嫻、《延南洞Global House》飾演姜宥娜，不知道大家有沒有印象呢？接下來她也確定與朴志訓、李新英合作新劇《遠看是藍色的春天》，期待她之後的表現啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e19d1c0e867ddee3bc9c118035133011/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894994.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e19d1c0e867ddee3bc9c118035133011%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894994.jpg&h=df849b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_28c3e28c6bfdf979a953112bc700cf2b/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133304-894995.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_28c3e28c6bfdf979a953112bc700cf2b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133304-894995.jpg&h=7bfc0e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖：SBS《張玉貞，為愛而生》、NAVER TV《A-TEEN 2》）<br />\n<br />\n（封面圖：IG@minah320_97）"},{"pid":"bd253f167f6b5bc883b26fbd3bf2febbde86a4fb","tid":2382210,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"好靚好kiyo<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52832b0a720f0e501329be70cdc57c6fe5c29f3f","tid":2382210,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd253f167f6b5bc883b26fbd3bf2febbde86a4fb","tid":2382210,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"好靚好kiyo<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:44:02.000Z","msg":"女神降臨d女角好正式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bd4a7eaac21f6fe811bee6e1077cefebbf2eb0","tid":2382210,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"係幾靚..."},{"pid":"805db249dddfad22f69bb05c8dcec7749654ef89","tid":2382210,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"係幾正...97年個樣成熟啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暗黑女二其實都好正"},{"pid":"1bb7b915d20eb491aca488671f0985d82d244b68","tid":2382210,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:42:28.000Z","msg"